    - "threading.Barrier.abort.__code__.co_name == 'abort'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Barrier.abort.__code__.co_argcount == 1. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Barrier.abort.__code__.co_varnames[0] == 'self'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
